[br]Just to look at things from the other side:

As an officer in my former guild I know what is a pain in the arse: Members that are always complaining about their epics.

A guild should be seen as a company... if the company is doing good, it is good for you. So you have to trust your leaders. If you do not trust, leave the guild, but stop the whining. 

And one other thing:
DO NOT WHINE IN /GU... pls refer to tells or chat channels.
