 can't use, which is a **** load goes to the guild bank.  This bank has never been touched it seems...  The leader has a horse btw, and is level 60.  That kind of made me wonder where he got all of his crap he has.  He does not have a lot of AA as well.  I can't blame this on him or anyone else, but the status on the bank makes me wonder.<br /><img src="images/shrug.gif" border="0" alt="" title="" align="middle" /></span></font></td>
